The paper proposes a method for obtaining sentence-level embeddings using a sequential encoder-decoder model for generating paraphrases. This falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML), which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category as it specifically deals with NLP tasks such as paraphrase generation. cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely as they cover ML techniques used in the paper. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are less likely but still possible as they cover neural network-based approaches and image-related tasks, respectively, which may be relevant to the proposed method.
